        "1.4.5": "<p>Fixes a fatal error, by removing the no longer relevant contextual help.<\/p>",
        "1.4.4": "<p>Bug fix and maintenance release. Enables &quot;pages and their children&quot; as a widget area condition.<\/p>",
        "1.4.3": "<p>Bug fix and maintenance release.<\/p>",
        "1.4.2": "<p>Security Fix for XSS vulnerability<\/p>",
        "1.4.1": "<p>Fixes an error notice on the homepage, caused by the tag check logic.<\/p>",
        "1.4.0": "<p>WordPress 3.8 compatibility.\nAdds &quot;posts tagged with&quot; condition.<\/p>",
        "1.3.1": "<p>Bug fix to ensure multiple conditions save correctly.<\/p>",
        "1.3.0": "<p>Optimisation update.<\/p>",
        "1.2.2": "<p>&quot;Widget Areas&quot; menu is now only visible to users who can add\/modify widgets.<\/p>",
        "1.2.1": "<p>Updated for WordPress 3.5+ compatibility. Adjusted &quot;Advanced&quot; tab logic. Fixed bug where &quot;Template Hierarchy -&gt; Pages&quot; condition wasn&#039;t being applied correctly. Dequeue WordPress SEO admin stylesheets from the &quot;Widget Areas&quot; &quot;Add&quot; and &quot;Edit&quot; screens.<\/p>",
        "1.2.0": "<p>Moved to WordPress.org. Woo! Added scope to methods and properties where missing.<\/p>"
    },
